The authors further defined age cohort 0, calculating the prevalence at the start and end of the interval, and subsequently, the cohort incidence for this age cohort. \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
